      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a simple way to get from A to B? This car has character and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it's an affordable entry point for anyone looking for a reliable workhorse or a first car to learn the ropes on.",
