    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a reliable driving experience for those who prioritize functionality over perfection. While the engine runs well and the transmission shifts through all gears, there are noticeable cosmetic imperfections, including some paint fading and minor interior upholstery wear. It has been a dependable commuter, though a potential buyer should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items like brake pad replacement and a minor oil leak. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
